@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_eyyigf(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = wp.cos(wp.sin(wp.sin(v0 + 0.44)))
    v2 = (wp.exp(0.70) + wp.abs(v0))
    v2 = (0.16 + ((v1 + 0.36 - v2 + 0.11) - wp.sin(tmp + 0.34)))
    tmp = tmp
    v1 = v0
    data[tid] = v0
